OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrain strikes could ruin   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChristmas, pub boss warns  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of the pub chain Fuller's has 
OL,6, told the BBC that rail strikes could   
OL,7, see Christmas parties cancelled unless 
OL,8, there is a "speedy resolution".        
OL,10,FSimon Emeny also warned that staff who 
OL,11,Frely on hours and tips over Christmas  
OL,12,Fcould suffer if there is a wave of     
OL,13,Fcancelled bookings.                    
OL,15,FHe urged the RMT to cancel the upcoming
OL,16,Fstrikes to make sure the sector "can   
OL,17,Fhave the Christmas it deserves".       
OL,19,FIt recently announced fresh strikes in 
OL,20,Fthe run-up to Christmas.               
